ther. </strong><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>And in the end.</strong><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 31, 31)\"><strong>She killed her own father.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><br><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">⚠CW: War, Death, Murder, Trauma⚠</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>| Theme song: \"</strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QXv1qDPWtx8&amp;ab_channel=GameTracks\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>KILL YOURSELF</strong></a>\" |<br><br><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-luqn5n css-j0re88 css-4g6ai3\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(50, 35, 65); margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/gfweb4.png\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">[\\\\\\\\Universe so far://\\]</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>[</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 31, 31)\"><strong>ACTIVE</strong></span><strong> DUTY:]</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">[//LOG-1: <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/9a69bf5f-4c13-42db-a3cc-4c837180d